{"tid":1861871,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藍絲醫院挑機被途人罵走","createTime":"2020-02-04T10:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T10:57:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3b8d83dcf4ff83749e6b8768a08e9f3a7fa3fc22","tid":1861871,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:34:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200204/EMET2R7I3UQ3PXA5R3Q353IKUA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200204%2FEMET2R7I3UQ3PXA5R3Q353IKUA%2F&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=436f7562\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200204%2FEMET2R7I3UQ3PXA5R3Q353IKUA%2F&h=05431e20\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200204/EMET2R7I3UQ3PXA5R3Q353IKUA/</a><br />\n<br />\n藍絲醫院挑機被途人罵走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】醫護罷工首日，普遍獲得公眾支持，亦有人不滿。一名中年男子昨日於廣華醫院外怒斥醫護罷工是為了趕走中國人，領取高薪卻罷工，但最終被途人罵走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200204/large/1580748843_b9c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200204%2Flarge%2F1580748843_b9c2.jpg&h=3ed4db47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名中年漢昨於廣華醫院外怒斥醫護罷工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市民：不值得為人禍犧牲<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：特首挑釁：極端手段唔會得逞<br />\n<br />\n昨午約4時，一名中年男子於廣華醫院外向罷工醫護指罵「唔係白衣天使，𠵱家着晒黑衫」，又斥醫護「咁高人工，要搞罷工？」認為封關只為趕走中國人。罷工醫護強調，只要政府全面封關，必定立即返回崗位工作，「我哋只係想政府全面封關，為嘅係香港人，唔係自己。」該名男子仍不斷指罵醫護，有途人忍不住為醫護平反：「你嗰啲係命，人哋嗰啲唔係命？」對面馬路更有多人高聲反駁，並向醫護表示支持「我撐你呀！」男子終悻悻然離開。<br />\n<br />\n其後，在尖沙嘴從事銷售員的盧小姐來到為罷工醫護人員加油，她說在網上看到有人批評廣華醫院外的罷工醫護，她特意前來支持，批評特首林鄭月娥遲遲不封關製造人禍，她認為醫護不值得為人禍犧牲，盧小姐言談間情緒激動，表示不願看到醫護被置於險地，更批評反對罷工的人自私，「冇理由推我哋啲人去死」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者趙雅婷"},{"pid":"e35edcf52a8cb30ba093aa26ce7aa91a1e52629a","tid":1861871,"uid":3149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:37:20.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b796b84f7bf09c1552b4d76242c45e8a8b35548","tid":1861871,"uid":2429,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/07/wFK4H0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F07%2FwFK4H0.png&h=34f10f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTqXb0P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTqXb0P.gif&h=31e53dd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43fe7ff16d0558f25f64ff8df9fbb1bb9696a39e","tid":1861871,"uid":194326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:39:01.000Z","msg":"個樣同個身形咁似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a30a11cf74b9de3916655299591914db9e67e2f","tid":1861871,"uid":79056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff17acf4999b09f80a0812b6e1bd9cba1e0670ae","tid":1861871,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43fe7ff16d0558f25f64ff8df9fbb1bb9696a39e","tid":1861871,"uid":194326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:39:01.000Z","msg":"個樣同個身形咁似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:39:53.000Z","msg":"好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8560cf530818898bc445e3928f94fb04ddabb829","tid":1861871,"uid":43553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:40:40.000Z","msg":"Push